{
  "stem": "4189.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there she was to meet the guide they would take her and some of the people during the night over the border.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They paid him some money for that and that's how they were supposed to go.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But when they got there they were caught by the German border patrol, and they were sent back to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So now we were in Belgium and my mother was back in Berlin, so we had to make a big decision.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Should we go back to Berlin, or should we stay and wait for another occasion that my mother could go again with another guide to get over the border?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we decided that they should stay because once we got out of Berlin, it would be best to stay, to stay in Belgium, and not to go back.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my mother could not go again to the-- to Aachen, to the border, because after that incidence, the border was tied up very tight.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They made it very difficult to cross the border illegally.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because many people did this before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were many people that managed to get into Belgian that way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But after that, they were not able to do this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my mother was stuck in Berlin, we were in Belgium, my uncle had this Visa to go to America where his ship was coming in.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And any day in the next few weeks, he had to leave.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were really desperate, and we didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So finally, they found out we had a distant relative that lived in Paris.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a French citizen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He lived in Paris all his life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we got in contact with him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, OK, send to children to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We will try to take care of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
